### Register a new user
POST {{base_url}}/users/register HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "username": "your_username",
  "password": "your_password",
  "email": "your_email"
}

###

### User login
POST {{base_url}}/users/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "username": "your_username",
  "password": "your_password"
}

###

### Retrieve current user's info
GET {{base_url}}/users/self HTTP/1.1

###

### Retrieve a specific user's info
GET {{base_url}}/users/{{user_id}} HTTP/1.1

###

### Update a specific user's info
PUT {{base_url}}/users/{{user_id}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "username": "new_username",
  "password": "new_password",
  "email": "new_email"
}

###

### Delete a specific user's profile
DELETE {{base_url}}/users/{{user_id}} HTTP/1.1
